    Title: Srimad Bhagavatam
    Location: XI iii
Tags:
  - Beauty-Peace=Peace=Serenity
---
The mind, when it is steady in divine contemplation, expresses sattwa
overcoming rajas and tamas. No more is there feverish hankering after
worldliness. Tranquillity comes to a heart which is no longer stirred by
desires, as stillness to a fire when no more fuel is added.
